# CI/CD Pipeline with Docker, GitHub Actions, and Docker Hub

![CI/CD Pipeline](https://github.com/Shalini1920/cicd-docker-project/actions/workflows/pipeline.yml/badge.svg)

## Project Overview

This project demonstrates a **complete CI/CD (Continuous Integration and Continuous Deployment) pipeline** using Docker and GitHub Actions.

Whenever code is pushed to the repository, GitHub Actions automatically:

1. Runs application tests
2. Builds a Docker image
3. Pushes the image to Docker Hub

This project simulates a real **DevOps workflow used in modern cloud environments.**

---

## Architecture


Developer Push Code
↓
GitHub
↓
GitHub Actions CI/CD
↓
Run Tests
↓
Build Docker Image
↓
Push Image to Docker Hub
↓
Deploy Container


---

## Tech Stack

- Python (Flask)
- Docker
- GitHub Actions
- Docker Hub
- Git

