## Docker Image

Docker Hub Repository:

https://hub.docker.com/r/shalzz19/cicd-app

---

## Running the Project Locally

### Pull the Docker image


docker pull shalzz19/cicd-app


### Run the container


docker run -p 5000:5000 shalzz19/cicd-app


Open in browser:


http://localhost:5000


---

## CI/CD Pipeline

The pipeline automatically performs:

- Code checkout
- Dependency installation
- Test execution
- Docker image build
- Docker image push to Docker Hub

This pipeline is implemented using **GitHub Actions**.

